---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Portfolio — Spirit Media Publishing" description="See what Kingdom authors are saying about Spirit Media Publishing. Client testimonials and success stories.">
  <main id="main-content">

    <!-- HERO -->
    <section class="bg-red-600 text-white py-24 px-4">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-red-200 mb-4">Client Stories</p>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold font-serif mb-6">Kingdom Authors. Real Results.</h1>
        <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-red-100 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Don't just take our word for it — hear directly from the authors whose messages we've helped publish and multiply around the world.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- VIDEO TESTIMONIALS -->
    <section class="bg-white py-20 px-4">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold font-serif text-gray-900 mb-4 text-center">Hear From Our Authors</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed text-center mb-12 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Watch these testimonials from authors who have published with Spirit Media.
        </p>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">

          <div>
            <div class="relative pb-[56.25%] h-0 overflow-hidden rounded-xl bg-gray-200">
              <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center">
                <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm font-medium">Video testimonial coming soon</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mt-3 text-center font-medium">Author Testimonial</p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <div class="relative pb-[56.25%] h-0 overflow-hidden rounded-xl bg-gray-200">
              <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center">
                <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm font-medium">Video testimonial coming soon</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mt-3 text-center font-medium">Author Testimonial</p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <div class="relative pb-[56.25%] h-0 overflow-hidden rounded-xl bg-gray-200">
              <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center">
                <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm font-medium">Video testimonial coming soon</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mt-3 text-center font-medium">Author Testimonial</p>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- WRITTEN TESTIMONIALS -->
    <section class="bg-gray-50 py-20 px-4">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold font-serif text-gray-900 mb-12 text-center">What Our Authors Say</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">

          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm p-6 flex flex-col">
            <div class="text-red-600 text-2xl mb-4">&ldquo;</div>
            <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6 flex-1">
              Spirit Media didn't just publish my book — they believed in my message when I wasn't sure I did.
            </p>
            <div class="border-t border-gray-100 pt-4">
              <p class="font-bold text-gray-900 text-sm">Pastor Marcus T.</p>
              <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm">Dallas, TX</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm p-6 flex flex-col">
            <div class="text-red-600 text-2xl mb-4">&ldquo;</div>
            <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6 flex-1">
              The process was so simple. I had no idea publishing could feel this supported.
            </p>
            <div class="border-t border-gray-100 pt-4">
              <p class="font-bold text-gray-900 text-sm">Dr. Angela P.</p>
              <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm">Atlanta, GA</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm p-6 flex flex-col">
            <div class="text-red-600 text-2xl mb-4">&ldquo;</div>
            <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6 flex-1">
              Kevin and Shelly are the real deal. They care about your calling, not just your manuscript.
            </p>
            <div class="border-t border-gray-100 pt-4">
              <p class="font-bold text-gray-900 text-sm">Pastor James W.</p>
              <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm">Chicago, IL</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm p-6 flex flex-col">
            <div class="text-red-600 text-2xl mb-4">&ldquo;</div>
            <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6 flex-1">
              I went from manuscript to Amazon in less than 4 weeks. Spirit Media delivered everything they promised.
            </p>
            <div class="border-t border-gray-100 pt-4">
              <p class="font-bold text-gray-900 text-sm">Sarah M.</p>
              <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm">Phoenix, AZ</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm p-6 flex flex-col">
            <div class="text-red-600 text-2xl mb-4">&ldquo;</div>
            <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6 flex-1">
              The marketing support is what sets Spirit Media apart. My book actually reached people.
            </p>
            <div class="border-t border-gray-100 pt-4">
              <p class="font-bold text-gray-900 text-sm">Bishop David L.</p>
              <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm">Houston, TX</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm p-6 flex flex-col">
            <div class="text-red-600 text-2xl mb-4">&ldquo;</div>
            <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6 flex-1">
              I was a first-time author with zero publishing experience. Spirit Media made me feel like a pro.
            </p>
            <div class="border-t border-gray-100 pt-4">
              <p class="font-bold text-gray-900 text-sm">Minister Renee C.</p>
              <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm">Charlotte, NC</p>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CALL TO ACTION -->
    <section class="bg-navy-950 text-white py-20 px-4 text-center">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold font-serif mb-6">Your Story Could Be Next</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Join the growing list of Kingdom authors who have published their message through Spirit Media Publishing.
        </p>
        <a href="/publishing" class="inline-block bg-red-600 text-white font-semibold px-6 py-3 rounded-md hover:bg-red-700 transition-colors">
          Start Your Publishing Journey
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

  </main>
</Layout>
